Mark my words, our lives are are going to look and feel very different going forward. Especially for our children. I don’t worry for myself anymore, but my kids and their kids.


Everyone will be a “medical patient” of the state. The state will mandate mass vaccination for everyone; flu shots, HPV, etc. Any new disease will have a vaccine that will become mandatory. https://www.rethink.org/new...


It used to take the opinion of three unrelated mental health professionals to commit someone. Now it only takes one. The have also changed maximum incarceration from 28 days to 12 weeks. This is under “emergency rules”.


My friend Jon Rappoport has exhaustively researched the validity of the test used to identify and quantify the Corona virus.


https://blog.nomorefakenews...


In this recent article he writes:


“ There are people (and I’m one of them) who challenge the claim that the PCR can show how much virus is in the patient’s body. The experts try to brush us off—we don’t understand the intricacies of the test, it’s highly technical, we’re not qualified to make a judgment, etc.


I’ve been searching for a way around this futile argument. In the process, I’ve discovered something important about the PCR. I SEE NO EVIDENCE THAT THE ACCURACY OF THE TEST HAS EVER BEEN PROVEN.”


I urge everyone to read this article. It will open your eyes as long as your mind is still open. However, the majority of people will not accept that the test is flawed. The populace worships at the alter of science as it once did with religion. Doctors and scientists in their white coats are the new priests in robes of our age. The believers are just as zealous as the perpetrators of the Spanish Inquisition. Any questioning of medical science is met with the same level of vitriol and fear that was once saved for the worst of the pagan heretics and questioners of the Christian faith.
I have known that one giant psy-ops was in the works for over a decade. Swine flu, SARS, Ebola, and Zika were merely a test of the waters. The architects of the Corona virus scare have learned their lesson. The biggest social media platforms; Twitter, Facebook, etc have been locked down. Website such as this one are rapidly disappearing from Google searches. In fact any searches looking for the truth are directed to mainstream media sites. Any questioning or dissension is met with immediate censure or ridicule from paid trolls.


In other words, we are in trouble folks. I don’t know how else to say it. Even many of those with whom I have always been able to discuss the frauds and lies that most of the world has bought into have been suckered into this whirlwind of fear. Wherever I go I can hear the drone of CNN, MSNBC, ABC, CBS, NBC, etc and their message of fear. Change the channel and message is the same. The population is all echoing the message- “We are all going to die...please save us government. We will give away all of our freedoms if you just save us!” I honestly cannot talk to anyone, and it occurs to me that I am now practicing “social distancing”. Not because of my fear of germs, mind you, but because I have lost my faith in humanity. I always say that I am the last generation of Americans who have had even an inkling of what personal freedom actually meant. God help us and please help my children!

snippet.textDisplay:
How long does it take to bring a new drug to market?
 
Johnson K. Gao
March 21, 2020
 
         On average, it takes at least ten years for a new medicine to complete the journey from initial discovery to the marketplace, with clinical trials alone taking six to seven years on average. The average cost to research and develop each successful drug is estimated to be $2.6 billion. See an article in detail. [1]
 
         Ten years to develop a new drug seems quite long. However, in compared with evolutionary scale, it is too short a time. The plant fern, such as wood fern Dryopteris, appeared on earth during the period of dinosaurs to live. [2]Some ferns are still living in the current world. They could be considered as living fossils. We know that dinosaurs lived in Jurassic Period (201 to 145 million years ago). During the Jurassic period, especially at higher latitudes, the warm, humid climate allowed lush jungles to cover much of the landscape. To my imagination the warm and humid climate is also favorable to germs to grow. In order not to let bacteria and virus damaging the body of the fern, fern must under went the natural selection process and to acquire the ability of producing antibiotics and antiviral substances. That is quite reasonable that Dryopteris root or fern rhizome, which has the Chinese herb name: 貫眾,has the characteristic of antibacterial, antiviral, anthelmintic. Please see “A review of the use of pteridophytes for treating human ailments”. See an article Anti-Influenza Virus (H5N1) Activity Screening on the Phloroglucinols from Rhizomes of Dryopteris crassirhizoma.[3]Use 10 (drug develop year needed)/145,000,000 (late Jurassic year) it produce 1/14,500,000. That means the ferns live now had spent 14.5 million times of drug development years needed to have invented the special antiviral “drug” in their root. Why don’t we use that drug to try to help us to anti corona virus and save the drug developmental time? Similarly, I had suggested using 板藍根(Radix Isatidis) to help us to anti coronavirus. See an article: Antiviral Activity ofIsatis indigotica Extract and Its Derived Indirubin against Japanese Encephalitis Virus. [4]
 
            Although I have not one hundred per cent confidence to say that my attached article and videos can cure or prevention coronavirus epidemic, at this point that there are no drug can cure that disease, we could only do this way: “死马当活马骑” (Riding over a dead horse as though riding on a life horse, i.e. a bad way is better than no way). Please watch my attached article and videos. [5, 6]
Literature cited

2. https://www.nhm.ac.uk/discover/when-did-dinosaurs-live.html
 
3. https://www.mdpi.com/1420-3049/22/3/431

snippet.textDisplay: Interesting ..I live here in Toronto Canada and it seems about 60% of the population is self isolating. I have been going to work daily and trying to follow my normal/ daily routine.  What I find fascinating is I saw way more people out and about with these symptoms in late January to Mid Feburary.  I wonder if alot of us during this time had a less robust strand of this or actually had it during this time and they either didnt know what it was or didnt tell us . Also anyone know what the incubation period is . For example right now I'm 100% healthy ..no cold no fever no cough no sneezing but I would had to think im still carrying anything around from mid February and could pass this along if im not self isolating. Much thanks for any input and stay safe perps . 👍

Definitely no fever though.
